# Telegram Chatbot â€“ Study Counseling & German Learning (Kyrgyz)

## Project Description

This project is a **Telegram chatbot** created to support **Kyrgyz-speaking users** with:

- Study counseling for universities in Germany
- Learning the German language with explanations in Kyrgyz

The chatbot aims to make information about studying and living in Germany more accessible and easier to understand.

---

## Target Audience

- Kyrgyz-speaking students who want to study in Germany
- People looking for guidance about:
  - Universities in Germany
  - Study programs
  - Application processes
  - Admission and language requirements
- German language learners who prefer explanations in Kyrgyz

---

## Features

- Telegram-based chatbot
- Study counseling:
  - General information about studying in Germany
  - Universities and higher education institutions
  - Application process and requirements
- German language learning:
  - Vocabulary explanations
  - Grammar explanations in Kyrgyz
  - Simple examples and dialogues
- Multilingual interaction (Kyrgyz / German)

---

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Telegram Bot API

